msgid "Assumption Checks"
msgstr "Pemeriksaan Asumsi"

msgid "Descriptives"
msgstr "Deskriptif"

msgid ""
"Vovk-Sellke Maximum <em>p</em>-Ratio: Based on a two-sided <em>p</em>-value,"
"the maximum possible odds in favor of H%1$s over H%2$s equals 1/(-e <em>p</"
"em> log(<em>p</em>)) for <em>p</em> %3$s .37 (Sellke, Bayarri, & Berger, "
"2001)."
msgstr ""
"Rasio-<em>p</em> Maksimum Vovk-Sellke: Berdasarkan nilai-<em>p</em> dua-"
"sisi,rasio maksimum yang mungkin mendukung H%1$s dibandingkan H%2$s sama "
"dengan 1/(-e <em>p</em>. log(<em>p</em>)) untuk <em>p</em> %3$s .37 (Sellke, "
"Bayarri, & Berger, 2001)."

msgid "Q-Q Plots"
msgstr "Diagram Q-Q"

msgid "Please provide another variable."
msgstr "Mohon tambahkan variabel lainnya."

msgid "Variables %1$s and %2$s are the same!"
msgstr "Variabel %1$s dan %2$s sama!"

msgid "Descriptives Plots"
msgstr "Diagram Deskriptif"

msgid "Bar Plots"
msgstr "Diagram Batang"

msgid "Group"
msgstr "Grup"

msgid "N"
msgstr "N"

msgid "Mean"
msgstr "Rerata"

msgid "SD"
msgstr "SD"

msgid "SE"
msgstr "SE"

msgid "Coefficient of variation"
msgstr "Koefisien dari variasi"

msgid "%.0f%% Credible Interval"
msgstr "%.0f%% Interval Kredibel"

msgid "Lower"
msgstr "Bawah"

msgid "Upper"
msgstr "Atas"

msgid "Inferential Plots"
msgstr "Diagram Inferensial"

msgid "Prior and Posterior"
msgstr "Priori dan Posterior"

msgid "Bayes Factor Robustness Check"
msgstr "Faktor Bayes dan Pemeriksaan Kekuatan"

msgid "Sequential Analysis"
msgstr "Analisis Sekuensial"

msgid ""
"Bayes factor robustness check plot currently not supported for informed "
"prior."
msgstr ""
"Diagram pemeriksaan kekuatan faktor Bayes saat ini tidak didukung untuk "
"priori terinformasi."

msgid ""
"Sequential analysis robustness check plot currently not supported for "
"informed prior."
msgstr ""
"Diagram pemeriksaan kekuatan analisis sekuensial saat ini tidak didukung "
"untuk priori terinformasi."

msgid "Expected numeric or character rscale but got %s."
msgstr "Diharapkan rscale numerik atau karakter tetapi terdapat %s."

msgid "Running robustness check %1$d / %2$d"
msgstr "Menjalankan pemeriksaan kekuatan %1$d / %2$d"

msgid "max BF%s"
msgstr "BF%s maks"

msgid "user prior"
msgstr "priori pengguna"

msgid "wide prior"
msgstr "priori lebar"

msgid "ultrawide prior"
msgstr "priori ultralebar"

msgid "BF%s"
msgstr "BF%s"

msgid "%1$s at r==%2$s"
msgstr "%1$s di r==%2$s"

msgid "Some Bayes factors were infinite"
msgstr "Beberapa faktor Bayes tidak terbatas"

msgid "Cauchy prior width"
msgstr "Lebar priori Cauchy"

msgid "Running sequential analysis %1$d / %2$d"
msgstr "Menjalankan analisis sekuensial %1$d / %2$d"

msgid "n"
msgstr "n"

msgid "Posterior"
msgstr "Posterior"

msgid "Prior"
msgstr "Priori"

msgid "%s%% CI:"
msgstr "%s%% CI:"

msgid "Effect size"
msgstr "Ukuran efek"

msgid "Raincloud Plots"
msgstr "Diagram Raincloud"

msgid "Raincloud Difference Plots"
msgstr "Diagram Perbedaan Raincloud"

msgid "Bayes factor could not be calculated"
msgstr "Faktor Bayes tidak dapat dikalkulasi"

msgid "Bayes factor is infinite"
msgstr "Faktor Bayes tanpa batas"

msgid "The Bayes factor is too small"
msgstr "Faktor Bayes terlalu kecil"

msgid ""
"t-value is large. A Savage-Dickey approximation was used to compute the "
"Bayes factor but no error estimate can be given."
msgstr ""
"nilai-t besar. Perkiraan Savage-Dickey digunakan untuk menghitung faktor "
"Bayes tetapi tidak ada estimasi galat yang dapat diberikan."

msgid "No error estimate is available for normal priors."
msgstr "Tidak ada estimasi galat tersedia untuk priori normal."

msgid "Bayesian Mann-Whitney U Test"
msgstr "Uji U Mann-Whitney Bayes"

msgid "Bayesian Independent Samples T-Test"
msgstr "Uji-T Sampel Independen Bayes"

msgid ""
"Result based on data augmentation algorithm with 5 chains of %.0f iterations."
msgstr ""
"Hasil berdasarkan algoritma augmentasi data dengan 5 rantai dari %.0f "
"iterasi."

msgid "error %%"
msgstr "galat %%"

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that the location of "
"group <em>%1$s</em> is greater than the location of group <em>%2$s</em>."
msgstr ""
"Untuk semua uji, hipotesis alternatif menentukan bahwa lokasi grup <em>%1$s</"
"em> lebih besar dari lokasi grup <em>%2$s</em>."

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that the location of "
"group <em>%1$s</em> is smaller than the location of group <em>%2$s</em>."
msgstr ""
"Untuk semua uji, hipotesis alternatif menentukan bahwa lokasi grup <em>%1$s</"
"em> lebih kecil dari lokasi grup <em>%2$s</em>."

msgid "Bayesian Wilcoxon Signed-Rank Test"
msgstr "Uji Peringkat Tertanda Wilcoxon Bayes"

msgid "Bayesian One Sample T-Test"
msgstr "Uji-T Satu Sampel Bayes"

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that the population mean "
"is greater than %s."
msgstr ""
"Untuk semua uji, hipotesis alternatif menentukan bahwa rerata populasi lebih "
"dari %s."

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that the population mean "
"is less than %s."
msgstr ""
"Untuk semua uji, hipotesis alternatif menentukan bahwa rerata populasi "
"kurang dari %s."

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that the population mean "
"differs from %s."
msgstr ""
"Untuk semua uji, hipotesis alternatif menentukan bahwa rerata populasi "
"berbeda dari %s."

msgid "Bayesian Paired Samples T-Test"
msgstr "Uji-T Sampel Terpasang Bayes"

msgid "Measure 1"
msgstr "Pengukuran 1"

msgid "Measure 2"
msgstr "Pengukuran 1"

msgid "Independent Samples T-Test"
msgstr "Uji-T Sample Independen"

msgid "Mann-Whitney U test."
msgstr "Uji U Mann-Whitney."

msgid "U"
msgstr "U"

msgid "Welch's t-test."
msgstr "Uji-t Welch."

msgid "t"
msgstr "t"

msgid "Student's t-test."
msgstr "Uji-t Student."

msgid "Statistic"
msgstr "Statistik"

msgid "Test"
msgstr "Uji"

msgid "df"
msgstr "df"

msgid "p"
msgstr "p"

msgid "Cohen's d"
msgstr "d Cohen"

msgid "Glass' delta"
msgstr "Delta Glass"

msgid "Hedges' g"
msgstr "g Hedge"

msgid "Mean Difference"
msgstr "Perbedaan Rerata"

msgid "Hodges-Lehmann Estimate"
msgstr "Estimasi Hodges-Lehmann"

msgid "Rank-Biserial Correlation"
msgstr "Korelasi Rank-Biserial"

msgid "Location Parameter"
msgstr "Parameter Lokasi"

msgid "Effect Size"
msgstr "Ukuran Efek"

msgid "Student t-test and Welch t-test"
msgstr "Uji-t Student dan uji-t Welch"

msgid "Student t-test"
msgstr "Uji-t Student"

msgid "Welch t-test"
msgstr "Uji-t Welch"

msgid "SE Difference"
msgstr "Perbedaan SE"

msgid ""
"For the %s, location parameter is given by mean difference. For the Mann-"
"Whitney test, location parameter is given by the Hodges-Lehmann estimate."
msgstr ""
"Untuk %s, parameter lokasi diberikan oleh perbedaan rerata. Untuk uji Mann-"
"Whitney, parameter lokasi diberikan oleh estimasi Hodges-Lehmann."

msgid "%1$s%% CI for %2$s"
msgstr "%1$s%% CI untuk %2$s"

msgid "SE %1$s"
msgstr "SE %1$s"

msgid ""
"For the Mann-Whitney test, effect size is given by the rank biserial "
"correlation."
msgstr ""
"Untuk uji Mann-Whitney, ukuran efek diberikan oleh korelasi biserial "
"peringkat."

msgid "For the %1$s, effect size is given by %2$s."
msgstr "Untuk %1$s, ukuran efek diberikan oleh %2$s."

msgid "Test of Normality (Shapiro-Wilk)"
msgstr "Uji Normalitas (Shapiro-Wilk)"

msgid "Residuals"
msgstr "Residu"

msgid "W"
msgstr "W"

msgid "Significant results suggest a deviation from normality."
msgstr "Hasil signifikan menyarankan deviasi dari normalitas."

msgid "Brown-Forsythe"
msgstr "Brown-Forsythe"

msgid "Levene's"
msgstr "Levene"

msgid "Test of Equality of Variances (%1$s)"
msgstr "Uji Kesetaraan Varians (%1$s)"

msgid "F"
msgstr "F"

msgid "%s<sub>1</sub>"
msgstr "%s<sub>1</sub>"

msgid "%s<sub>2</sub>"
msgstr "%s<sub>2</sub>"

msgid "greater"
msgstr "lebih"

msgid "less"
msgstr "kurang"

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that group %1$s is %2$s "
"than group %3$s."
msgstr ""
"Untuk semua uji, hipotesis alternatif menentukan bahwa grup %1$s %2$s dari "
"grup %3$s."

msgid ""
"Brown-Forsythe test is significant (p < .05), suggesting a violation of the "
"equal variance assumption"
msgstr ""
"Uji Brown-Forsythe signifikan (p < .05), menyarankan pelanggaran dari asumsi "
"varians sama"

msgid ""
"Levene's test is significant (p < .05), suggesting a violation of the equal "
"variance assumption"
msgstr ""
"Uji Levene signifikan (p < .05), menyarankan pelanggaran asumsi kesamaan "
"varians"

msgid ""
"Glass' delta uses the standard deviation of group %1$s of variable %2$s."
msgstr "Delta Glass menggunakan deviasi standar grup %1$s variabel %2$s."

msgid "F-statistic could not be calculated"
msgstr "Statistik-F tidak dapat dikalkulasi"

msgid "Group Descriptives"
msgstr "Deskriptif Grup"

msgid "Mean Rank"
msgstr "Peringkat Rerata"

msgid "Sum Rank"
msgstr "Peringkat Jumlah"

msgid "One Sample T-Test"
msgstr "Uji-T Satu Sampel"

msgid "Wilcoxon signed-rank test."
msgstr "Uji peringkat tertanda Wilcoxon."

msgid "V"
msgstr "V"

msgid "Z test."
msgstr "Uji Z."

msgid "Z"
msgstr "Z"

msgid "Location Difference"
msgstr "Perbedaan Lokasi"

msgid "Student t-test and Z-test"
msgstr "Uji-t dan uji-Z Student"

msgid "Z-test"
msgstr "Uji-Z"

msgid ""
"For the %s, location difference estimate is given by the sample mean "
"difference <em>d</em>. For the Wilcoxon test, location difference estimate "
"is given by the Hodges-Lehmann estimate."
msgstr ""
"Untuk %s, estimasi perbedaan lokasi diberikan oleh <em>d</em> perbedaan "
"rerata sampel. Untuk uji Wilcoxon, estimasi perbedaan lokasi diberikan oleh "
"estimasi Hodges-Lehmann."

msgid "For the Student t-test, effect size is given by Cohen's <em>d</em>."
msgstr "Untuk uji-t Student, ukuran efek diberikan oleh <em>d</em> Cohen."

msgid ""
"For the Wilcoxon test, effect size is given by the matched rank biserial "
"correlation."
msgstr ""
"Untuk uji Wilcoxon, ukuran efek diberikan oleh korelasi biserial peringkat "
"tercocok."

msgid ""
"For the Z test, effect size is given by Cohen's <em>d</em> (based on the "
"provided population standard deviation)."
msgstr ""
"Untuk uji Z, ukuran efek diberikan oleh <em>d</em> Cohen (berdasarkan "
"deviasi standar populasi tersedia)."

msgid "greater than"
msgstr "lebih besar dari"

msgid "less than"
msgstr "kurang dari"

msgid "different from"
msgstr "beda dari"

msgid ""
"For the %1$s, the alternative hypothesis specifies that the mean is %2$s "
"%3$s."
msgstr ""
"Untuk %1$s, hipotesis alternatif menentukan bahwa rerata adalah %2$s %3$s."

msgid ""
"For the Wilcoxon test, the alternative hypothesis specifies that the median "
"is %1$s %2$s."
msgstr ""
"Untuk uji Wilcoxon, hipotesis alternatif menentukan bahwa median adalah %1$s "
"%2$s."

msgid ""
"CI could not be computed for effect size, due to low sample size and/or "
"extreme effect size."
msgstr ""
"CI tidak dapat dihitung untuk ukuran efek, karena ukuran sampel rendah dan/"
"atau ukuran efek ekstrim."

msgid ""
"Sample size too small for desired confidence level. Using %.1f%% instead"
msgstr ""
"Ukuran sampel terlalu kecil untuk tingkat kepercayaan yang diinginkan. "
"Menggunakan %.1f%% sebagai gantinya"

msgid "Paired Samples T-Test"
msgstr "Uji-T Sampel Terpasang"

msgid "z"
msgstr "z"

msgid ""
"For the Student t-test, location parameter is given by mean difference "
"<em>d</em>. For the Wilcoxon test, location parameter is given by the Hodges-"
"Lehmann estimate."
msgstr ""
"Untuk uji-t Student, parameter lokasi diberikan oleh <em>d</em> perbedaan "
"rerata. Untuk uji Wilcoxon, parameter lokasi diberikan oleh estimasi Hodges-"
"Lehmann."

msgid ""
"For the Student t-test, effect size is given by Cohen's <em>d</em>. For the "
"Wilcoxon test, effect size is given by the matched rank biserial correlation."
msgstr ""
"Untuk uji-t Student, ukuran efek diberikan oleh <em>d</em> Cohen. Untuk uji "
"Wilcoxon, ukuran efek diberikan oleh korelasi biserial peringkat tercocok."

msgid "Cohen's d corrected for correlation between observations."
msgstr "d Cohen dikoreksikan untuk korelasi antara observasi."

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that Measure 1 is less "
"than Measure 2."
msgstr ""
"Untuk semua uji, hipotesis alternatif menentukan bahwa Pengukuran 1 kurang "
"dari Pengukuran 2."

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that Measure 1 is "
"greater than Measure 2."
msgstr ""
"Untuk semua uji, hipotesis alternatif menentukan bahwa Pengukuran 1 lebih "
"dari Pengukuran 2."

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that %1$s is less than "
"%2$s."
msgstr ""
"Untuk semua uji, hipotesis alternatif menentukan bahwa %1$s kurang dari %2$s."

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that %1$s is greater "
"than %2$s."
msgstr ""
"Untuk semua uji, hipotesis alternatif menentukan bahwa %1$s lebih dari %2$s."

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that Measure 1 is less "
"than Measure 2. For example, %1$s is less than %2$s."
msgstr ""
"Untuk semua uji, hipotesis alternatif menentukan bahwa Pengukuran 1 kurang "
"dari Pengukuran 2. Contohnya, %1$s kurang dari %2$s."

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that Measure 1 is "
"greater than Measure 2. For example, %1$s is greater than %2$s."
msgstr ""
"Untuk semua uji, hipotesis alternatif menentukan bahwa Pengukuran 1 lebih "
"dari Pengukuran 2. Contohnya, %1$s lebih dari %2$s."

msgid "The following pair is duplicated: %s"
msgid_plural "The following pairs are duplicated: %s"
msgstr[0] "Pasangan berikut digandakan: %s"
